ZH: 这是医生开的药，记得按时服用。
EN: This is the medicine prescribed by the doctor, remember to take it on time.

ZH: 我昨天吃了一颗止痛药，感觉好多了。
EN: I took a painkiller yesterday and felt much better.

ZH: 爷爷每天都要吃降压药来控制血压。
EN: Grandpa has to take blood pressure medication every day to control his blood pressure.

ZH: 这种感冒药对儿童比较安全。
EN: This cold medicine is safer for children.

ZH: 我的药盒里装着各种各样的药片。
EN: My pillbox contains a variety of pills.

ZH: 这种药膏能有效缓解皮肤瘙痒。
EN: This ointment can effectively relieve skin itching.

ZH: 这种草药对头痛有一定的疗效。
EN: This herbal medicine has a certain effect on headaches.

ZH: 这款食疗药材对于调理身体很有帮助。
EN: This dietary medicine is very helpful in conditioning the body.

ZH: 这种药水用来洗伤口可以防止感染。
EN: This medicine is used to wash wounds to prevent infection.

ZH: 这种药有助于提高免疫力。
EN: This medicine helps improve immunity.

ZH: 要注意这种药可能会有副作用。
EN: Be aware that this medicine may have side effects.

ZH: 他的药片放在一个小药盒里。
EN: His pills are stored in a small pillbox.

ZH: 这种药膏可以用来涂抹在受伤的部位上。
EN: This ointment can be applied to the injured area.

ZH: 西药和中药在治疗疾病上有不同的作用。
EN: Western medicine and traditional Chinese medicine have different effects on treating diseases.

ZH: 这种保健品是中药材研制而成的。
EN: This health product is made from traditional Chinese medicinal materials.

ZH: 她的祖母擅长使用各种中药调理身体。
EN: Her grandmother is good at using various Chinese medicinal herbs to regulate the body.

ZH: 这种药物对于治疗慢性疾病有较好的效果。
EN: This medication has a good effect on treating chronic diseases.

ZH: 这种药剂可以改善体内的微循环。
EN: This medication can improve microcirculation in the body.

ZH: 在家庭药箱里要备有必备的常用药物。
EN: Essential medications should be prepared in the family medicine cabinet.

ZH: 这种药膏有助于加快伤口愈合速度。
EN: This ointment helps speed up wound healing.
